org.apache.paimon.flink.compact

Class MultiTableScanBase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.compact.MultiTableScanBase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the result of scanning file :
    1. Tuple2<Split,String> for the table with multi buckets, such as dynamic or fixed bucket table.
    2. MultiTableUnawareAppendCompactionTask for the table witch fixed single bucket ,such as unaware bucket table.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiAwareBucketTableScan, MultiUnawareBucketTableScan

    public abstract class MultiTableScanBase<T>
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    This class is responsible for implementing the scanning logic for the table of different type buckets during compaction.
